org.mobicents.slee.runtime.facilities
Class TracerStorage

java.lang.Object
  org.mobicents.slee.runtime.facilities.TracerStorage

public class TracerStorage
extends java.lang.Object

This class holds tracers for sources. By default it create root tracer. It implicitly creates ancestor tracers for requested name. It holds reference TraceName->TracerImpl. It also associates parent to a child.
Start time:19:20:19 2009-03-09
Project: mobicents-jainslee-server-core
